     H            Y.
     F** EJKR64 **************************************************
     F* B2B_S  GET RECORD FORMAT LENGTH                          *
      *  T.SAKAKI            2016.11.20                          *
     F* -------------------------------------------------------  *
     F* (JW) CREATE QTEMP/EJKWP64 TO COMPILE THIS PROGRAM.       *
     F* EX.  DSPFD  FILE(HFILE1/AB#PPCT) TYPE(*RCDFMT) +         *
     F*             OUTPUT(*OUTFILE) OUTFILE(QTEMP/EJKWP64)      *
     F************************************************************
     FEJKWP64 IF  E                    DISK
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@LEN   50
     C*
     C           1         SETLLEJKWP64
     C                     READ EJKWP64                  55
     C           *IN55     IFEQ '0'
     C                     Z-ADDRFLEN     P@LEN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
